# Case Study — Tethering in NFZ Approval (Significant change)

> This documents the real timeline and process of applying for tethering in NFZ 
> approval under an existing ReOC. Company details are anonymised.
>
> **Operator:** Small commercial operator, Sydney metro area  
> **ReOC fleet:** Sub-250g, 250g-2kg, and sub-25kg multirotor   
> **Operation types:** Building wash

---

